{
  "stem": "13833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I says, Uncle, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then he told me this story, that he was the one who came up at  3 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I asked the ambassador, and all four of them survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was a funny feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it happened to Ambassador [NON-ENGLISH] too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was already a consul in Vienna, in 1956, when the uprising was from the other people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he figured, why don't I do what Raoul does?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I go down to the Danube-- because they came on the boat-- and I help people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they went down again with the Red Cross trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And out comes a lady, and he sees-- we don't remember these people, but they remember us, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the lady starts running and says, Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] you saved me from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now you're saving me from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it-- it was a great feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, of course, the last big, big thing what happened was two weeks before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's why I had to stop working, because I got a little pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Three days, Eichmann ordered the Hungarian Nazis to kill the Jews into the Danube, because they will die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In 40 years, it was never that cold in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were big icicles in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They roped three together, and they shot the middle one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So naturally, all three fell in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them got out by themselves, but very few.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the third day, Raoul was out saving people somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, what will Eichmann say next?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How many of you can swim?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was the only one who put up my hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, let's go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no idea where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very dark, starless night.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
